<paragraph id="IFRS15_IE37" base="F31740172"><paranum>IE37</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="IE37"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0938">An entity, a construction company, enters into a contract to construct a commercial building for a customer on customer-owned land for promised consideration of CU1 million and a bonus of CU200,000 if the building is completed within 24 months. The entity accounts for the promised bundle of goods and services as a single performance obligation satisfied over time in accordance with <xref id="IFRS15_X1163" base="F33216800" href="IFRS15_35.dita#IFRS15_35">paragraph 35(b) of IFRS 15</xref> because the customer controls the building during construction. At the inception of the contract, the entity expects the following:</p><table id="IFRS15_TAB0002" base="SL31740220" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="30*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="15*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="C3" colwidth="55*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><tbody><row keep_together="3"><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRS15_P0939" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0940" typeface="sansserif"><b>CU</b></p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0941" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0942" typeface="sansserif">Transaction price</p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0943" typeface="sansserif">1,000,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0944" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0945" typeface="sansserif">Expected costs</p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0946" typeface="sansserif">700,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0947" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0948" typeface="sansserif">Expected profit (30%)</p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" double_underline="yes" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0949" typeface="sansserif">300,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0950" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>